WEBVTT

00:43.280 --> 00:47.501
PRUDIE: The old grey duck,
she stole her nest

00:47.680 --> 00:51.138
And laid up in the fields
THOLLY: ..in the fields

00:51.320 --> 00:55.097
PRUDIE: And when the young ones,
they came forth

00:55.280 --> 00:58.784
They had no tails nor bills

00:59.200 --> 01:03.227
They had no tails, nor bills...
- What's that, out there?

01:04.120 --> 01:05.587
- Th...
- What?

01:05.760 --> 01:07.739
PRUDIE: Be they ours?

01:16.320 --> 01:18.299
French.

01:19.200 --> 01:20.827
Lord, save us.

01:21.560 --> 01:23.824
PRUDIE: Attack. Attack!

01:24.000 --> 01:29.142
The Frenchies are coming! Ring a bell!
The Frenchies are coming!

01:29.320 --> 01:32.585
- Attack! The Frenchies are coming!
- (Bell clangs)

01:32.760 --> 01:34.421
The Frenchies are coming!

01:34.600 --> 01:37.023
- The Frenchies are coming!
- (Panicked shouting)

01:38.120 --> 01:40.680
(Church bell ringing)

01:42.040 --> 01:45.020
(Shouting and bell ringing)

01:48.560 --> 01:51.461
The Frenchies are coming!
They're coming!

01:51.640 --> 01:53.619
The Frenchies are coming...

01:55.840 --> 01:57.740
(Excited chatter)

02:01.160 --> 02:02.980
(Crowd falls silent)

02:03.160 --> 02:05.025
(Muttering)

02:05.200 --> 02:08.704
PRUDIE: Where have they gone?
- They'll be spying out our defences.

02:08.880 --> 02:11.303
But...they'll be back.

02:14.480 --> 02:17.301
SIR FRANCIS: This threat from the French
cannot be ignored.

02:17.480 --> 02:22.349
Cornwall is woefully unprepared
for an enemy which is now at our door.

02:22.520 --> 02:24.067
Those men with military experience

02:24.240 --> 02:26.879
will form and train
companies of volunteers

02:27.040 --> 02:31.704
to quell threat and disorder
wherever it appears.

02:31.880 --> 02:35.304
When the hour comes - and come it will -

02:35.480 --> 02:37.186
we must not be found wanting.

02:37.360 --> 02:40.022
(Muttering)

02:40.200 --> 02:42.100
Truro is a key location.

02:42.280 --> 02:44.259
(Low chatter)

